data.description: Contract Pending. Welcome to this beautiful Dutch Colonial home, a picturesque two-story gem that boasts classic charm and modern updates. The main floor features a cozy living space, dining room, kitchen, office and one of the bedrooms. Upstairs you'll find two more bedrooms, one with a loft and full bathroom. There are lots of new updates including new carpet and vinyl flooring in the kitchen, office, dining, living room and stairs. Exterior updates include new vinyl siding on shed, garage and house addition. There are also new shutters, exterior paint, front stoop and back stoop. The privacy fence was replaced in 2020. To complete the outdoor space, there are two storage sheds and great patio space. Make your appointment today!
